# Set up a minimal desktop environment on Devuan linux

1. download the minimal boot iso
2. install the system (standard system utilities and ssh server but *no desktop env*)
3. sudo apt install lxde uxterm
4. install a nice font:
   - run: `sudo apt install xfonts-terminus && xset fp rehash && xlsfonts | grep terminus`
   - follow this: https://www.genunix.com/dclarke/termingus/readme.txt
